title: Did Antepha say "in favour" of winning as supporters, Trump and the riot after election day?
subtitle: These supposed plans seem to have been online for years.
author: Nur Ibrahim
vclaim: There is an Antepha that calls on the "public" to hide themselves as supporters of US President Donald Trump and the riots on November 4, 2020, one day after the American elections, so that the media and the police blame the Trump supporters for the violence.
